      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from a single production lot were tested across two independent laboratories. Lot certificates, dimensional inspection records, and material certificates were retained. Sample-to-sample variability (CV <5% for stiffness) is consistent with manufacturing tolerances."
