      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration at a fixed load angle. While the protocol is standardised and clinically representative, only one test condition was employed, limiting the breadth of validation evidence. Achieved level (2) is below the required level (3); this shortfall is noted and accepted given the standardised nature of the F1717 protocol and corroborating multi-laboratory data."
