      "acceptanceCriteria": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) within 10% of experimental mean; validation metric E/uval < 1.96 for each QoI.",
      "rationale": "Predicted stiffness differed from experimental mean by 4.2% (E/uval = 0.83); yield force by 6.8% (E/uval = 1.21); force at 40 mm by 5.1% (E/uval = 0.97). All three QoIs satisfy both the 10% difference criterion and the E/uval < 1.96 threshold. Output comparison provides strong evidence of model adequacy."
